messages.text: I thought you might be gone already.
I wanted to see you again.
No. Catching a ride with Steph.
Ur the one who texts and drives.
Don’t you leave for college tomorrow?
Sarah. I just need see u one last time.
I’ve made my peace with it.
Ur the one who can’t do long distance.
Gabe. Why r u doing this?
That means Steph has to take the pond road.
All I can see are tire tracks going off the road.
Have you been at Jones this whole time?
Do I? It’s foggy down here.
She’s going to drop me off.
It’s just a half a mile walk.
2 b truthful. I was kind of hoping you would text.
Was it just a fling to u?
Close. I can hear the water.
Remember when we met? You were swimming.
And you swam out so far.
All the way from my parent’s dock.
Can u see my parent’s dock now?
Mist is clearing. Is that you?
I thought your parents sold that place.
I thought we were going to say goodbye.
I can’t see u anymore. The mist is closing in.
The one that went off the road.
No. Gabe. Why r u doing this?
I think I loved you too.
